{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-strava-activities","description":"Gatsby plugin that fetches athlete activities from Strava","keywords":["gatsby","strava","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"doconnor","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/be9f6f09b281c50312f12bf9b2483026"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/danoc/gatsby-source-strava-activities"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-strava-activities\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-strava-activities\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-strava-activities</h1>\n<p>A Gatsby plugin that fetches athlete activities from Strava’s <code class=\"language-text\">/athlete/activities</code> endpoint. <a href=\"https://developers.strava.com/docs/reference/#api-Activities-getLoggedInAthleteActivities\">Learn more about the endpoint</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Install <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-source-strava-activities</code> in your project with <code class=\"language-text\">yarn add gatsby-source-strava-activities</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">npm install gatsby-source-strava-activities</code>.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add the plugin to your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> file:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\">\n      <pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby-source-strava-activities\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// This is the \"Access Token\" from:</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// https://www.strava.com/settings/api</span>\n    authToken<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// [Optional] An epoch timestamp to use for filtering activities that have taken place after a certain time.</span>\n    after<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// An epoch timestamp to use for filtering activities that have taken place before a certain time.</span>\n    before<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The plugin will store the Strava API response in Gatsby. You can grab the activities with a query such as:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\">\n      <pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allStravaActivity <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        activity <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          name\n          id\n          distance\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>The node contains the <a href=\"https://developers.strava.com/docs/reference/#api-Activities-getLoggedInAthleteActivities\">entire response from Strava’s endpoint</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-strava-activities/","id":"d41cbc4d-15e1-57b3-8066-330b5d765847"}}